Gan '''Waman''' [[ablulu]] akk iggutn ɣ iggi n [[Akal (Amtiwg)|Wakal]]. Dn 70% n wudn n [[Akal (Amtiwg)|wakal]].

Aman ɣusnin, ur darsn taḍfi, tujjut, ula aklu. gan ɣ txssa n [[Afgan|ufgan]] imqqurn 65 %, dar wazzan 75 %, dar ubijju n krad yirn 95 %. Gan iggi n wakal 70 % ilin gis 97 % n waman malḥnin d 3 % mmimnin. ɣ twuriwin n takrura ar nsawal f talɣa '''H<sub>2</sub>O''' macc ɣwid gan aman ɣusnin ur gisn kra tn issṛiẓn. Gin waman yat tɣawsa lli isfsayn kraygat anaw n lmεdn niɣ aẓru.
Mac aman lli nttafa ɣ iggi n wakal ur jju gin tanga iɣusn 100% illa bdda gis imik n zɣ tangiwin yaḍnin.

